data.description: This is your chance to live in the very desirable Belmont Lake Preserve! Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom traditional style home. Main living area features an open concept style. Kitchen has center Island, bar, gas range, refrigerator, microwave, dishwasher with walk in pantry and a separate formal dining room or it can be used as an office. Family room features a gas log fireplace, Luxury vinyl plank flooring through out. Walk right out to the private partly wooded back yard, enjoy the quite cul-du-sack with beautiful mature pine trees, with plenty of yard for family gatherings and pets. Second floor features the bedrooms, storage closets, laundry room. The owners suite has a generously large walk in closet, walk in shower and room that has space for a quite seating area.
